FIGURES 10–11. 
<taxonomicName authority="(Bezzi, 1909)" authorityName="Bezzi" authorityYear="1909" baseAuthorityName="Bezzi" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[345,720,683,706]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Crossopalpus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="120" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="armipes">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[345,576,683,706]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="120">Crossopalpus armipes</emphasis>
(Bezzi, 1909)
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Holotype ♀, SMTD). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[961,992,683,705]" pageId="9" pageNumber="120">10.</emphasis>
Lateral habitus; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1165,1194,683,705]" pageId="9" pageNumber="120">11.</emphasis>
